OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FHis first shot, towards the bottom-
OL,7,Fright corner, was saved by Croatian
OL,8,Fgoalkeeper Dominik Livakovic, but it
OL,9,Fwas a retake of the penalty that gave
OL,10,FKane his first goal.
OL,12,FITV News breaks down what happened.
OL,14,FWhy did Kane have to retake the
OL,15,Fpenalty?
OL,17,FKane was able to retake his first
OL,18,Ffailed penalty attempt after two
OL,19,FCroatian players were caught
OL,20,Fencroaching thanks to the video
OL,21,Fassistant referee (VAR).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FGoalkeepers must keep at least one
OL,7,Ffoot on the goal line until the
OL,8,Fpenalty taker has touched the ball,
OL,9,Fbut in this case, Livakovic stepped
OL,10,Fforward early.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FCroatian defender Josko Gvardiol, who
OL,18,Fplays for Manchester City, was also
OL,19,Ffound to have encroached on the 18-
OL,20,Fyard line, after he prematurely ran
OL,21,Finto the penalty box.
OL,26,@qD@[rq
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
