PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FThis alone doesn't mean an automatic
OL,7,Fretake, but because England's Noni
OL,8,FMadueke was behind Gvardiol, the
OL,9,Fdefender's move prevented attacker
OL,10,FMadueke from getting a shot from the
OL,11,Frebound.
OL,13,FIf a violation takes place during a
OL,14,Fpenalty and it isn't scored, it must
OL,15,Fbe retaken, according to International
OL,16,FFootball Association Board (IFAB)
OL,17,Frules.
OL,19,FKane's second attempt then secured
OL,20,FEngland's first goal of the game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
