PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FWhat has Kane said about it?
OL,8,FKane has admitted he stuttered on
OL,9,Fpurpose when taking his first penalty,
OL,10,Fhaving studied Livakovic's play and
OL,11,Fdecided it might make him step forward
OL,12,Fearly.
OL,14,FHe told the BBC: "When I watched the
OL,15,Fclips, I saw he likes to move early,
OL,16,Fso I knew that there was a chance that
OL,17,Fif I did the stutter that he would
OL,18,Fcome off the line.
OL,26,@rD@Xrq
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,F"I was 80% sure that it was off the
OL,7,Fline, I wasn't 100% sure, then
OL,8,Fobviously when it got retaken I
OL,9,Fchanged the technique a little bit.
OL,11,F"This is all why I do the research,
OL,12,Fand in the end it worked out nicely
OL,13,Ffor me."
OL,15,FHas Kane had to retake a penalty
OL,16,Fbefore?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FKane had to retake a penalty after a
OL,7,Fsimilar violation not long ago, when
OL,8,Fplaying for Bayern Munich against
OL,9,FItalian side Atalanta in March this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe striker had stuttered in his run-
OL,13,Fup to the first penalty, which was
OL,14,Fsaved by goalkeeper Marco Sportiello.
OL,16,FA VAR assessment then found that
OL,17,FSportiello had come off his line early
OL,18,Fand it was retaken, this time
OL,19,Fresulting in a goal for Kane.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
