FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781779675
OL,3,CWhy did England's Harry Kane have to
OL,4,Cretake penalty against Croatia?
OL,6,FAfterwards, Kane said he knew
OL,7,FSportiello liked to come off his line,
OL,8,Fsaying: "I knew that if I stopped,
OL,9,Fthere was a good chance he'd come too
OL,10,Ffar forward. And that's exactly what
OL,11,Fhappened.
OL,13,F"You can tell from my reaction that I
OL,14,Fwanted to take it again straight away."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
